-- Sasol Lures Interest of Potential Buyers for Fertilizer Blending Plants
-- Carli Lourens
-- 2010-07-14T10:19:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/sasol-lures-interest-of-potential-buyers-for-fertilizer-blending-plants.html

          
          
             Sasol Ltd., South Africa’s largest
ammonia supplier, has received queries from parties interested
in buying fertilizer blending facilities it plans to sell as
part of an agreement with the country’s Competition Commission,
spokeswoman Jacqui O’Sullivan said in a text message today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Johannesburg at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        